snippet.title: Bhagavanth Kesari - Trailer | Nandamuri Balakrishna | Anil Ravipudi | Kajal | Sree Leela |Thaman S
snippet.description:
Presenting the Massive Trailer of Bhagavanth Kesari (Telugu), a first-of-its-kind actioner with a novel script starring Nandamuri Balakrishna in the Lead Role and also co stars Kajal Aggarwal, Sreeleela and Arjun Rampal. 

The film has been Written and Directed by Anil Ravipudi. Music composed by SS Thaman. Cinematography helmed by C Ram Prasad and Proudly Produced by Sahu Garapati and Harish Peddi under Shine Screens Cinema Banner. This film Presents NBK Like Never Before and is scheduled for its theatrical release for October 19th.

Chore haryaane wale gaad denge lathh
Hilee gaadi ghani chori baithi gail mhaare gachh
Kit bhaajega re bighey kille kulley saale att
6 feeet bheethar gaand devein pavega na bach
X2 
Verse 1 :--
Tu apne khappetraan tey puch mera toraaa 
1 no baatcheet hariyaaane ka choraa 
Bulaa liye tu jitne bhi gail badmaash tere 
Gaad denge 6 feet jo bhi chodaaa hora 
Hukka paani chaaley mhara bhai kati mauj mein
Killey ghane naam piseyy le rhya hu mauj me 
Jaan den wale rahein gail kati loyal rakhta na 
G**du ne kadey apni faouj me , 

Me jit jaaun 
Wdeyy bajje danka haryaane ka 
Baccha budhaaaa shokeeeni 
Raagni uchii gaaane kaaa
Desi ghee me chormaa tadke haudi pe nahane ka
Or bhaduuon ka kaaam
Pacche thokkar tezzz khane kaaakaaa

Pehlwaan chore guddiyaa pe mote batt
Daao laga dhed dhrti me hoja bhataa bhaattt
Mhara naam jo naa jaaane vo bhi leve naam rattt
Aaati deekh G wagon aaati aandhi te Tu bachhhhhh
Hoook
Chore haryaane wale gaad denge lathh
Hilee gaadi ghani chori baithi gail mhaare gachh
Kit bhaajega re bighey kille kulley saale att
6 feeet bheethar gaand devein  pavega na bach
X2 
Verse 2 :--

Door te pehchana jaa manas  haryaane ka
Kaam mhaara haathi ka kutto ka bhonke jaane ka

Minta me todeein gend aakeyy saaley teri kaaale khaaa
 kaam mhara

 dum itna  raaaakhey  ad jyaa 
duniyaa pe hukum chalane ka

kaaadu bhooot 
mere saaaale kaaa

snippet.title: Ayalaan - Official Teaser | Sivakarthikeyan | A.R.Rahman | Rakul Preet Singh | R.Ravikumar
snippet.description:
Presenting the Official Teaser of "Ayalaan", Starring Sivakarthikeyan and Rakul Preet Singh in the lead roles. Directed by R. Ravikumar and produced by 24AM Studios & Music by A.R. Rahman.

Ayalaan is a science-fiction movie that promises to take you on a thrilling ride to space. The film features music composed by A.R. Rahman. Get ready to witness an epic adventure like never before with Ayalaan.

To the fearless warriors of the skies, a very Happy Indian Air Force Day! 
#IndianAirForceDay

snippet.title: Israel 'at war' as Hamas militants launch surprise attack

snippet.description:
#lokeshkanagaraj #leo #vijay 

Welcome to the Cinema Vikatan YouTube Channel, your premier destination for all things cinema. In this electrifying episode, we have a sensational treat for you as we present an exclusive interview with none other than the visionary director, Lokesh Kanagaraj.

Lokesh Kanagaraj, the mastermind behind some of the most compelling and impactful films in recent times, delves deep into the much-anticipated "Leo," his latest directorial venture starring the enigmatic Actor Vijay. Get ready for an in-depth discussion as Lokesh Kanagaraj takes you behind the scenes of "Leo," revealing fascinating insights into the making of this highly-awaited film.

From the creative process to the challenges faced during production, Lokesh Kanagaraj provides a glimpse into the world of "Leo" that you won't find anywhere else. His unique storytelling and cinematic vision promise an unforgettable experience for audiences, and this interview is your backstage pass to all the action.

Stay tuned, as Lokesh Kanagaraj shares his thoughts, experiences, and passion for storytelling in the world of Indian cinema. Like, share, and subscribe to the Cinema Vikatan YouTube Channel to stay updated on this exclusive interview and other engaging content that offers an inside look into the magic of cinema.

Don't miss this opportunity to discover what makes "Leo" and Lokesh Kanagaraj's directorial prowess so remarkable. Welcome to Cinema Vikatan, where every episode is a journey into the heart and soul of filmmaking.

Episode 3896: Bhakti Ka Vachan
--------------------------------------------------------
 Bhakti pleads that the Gokuldham residents allow her to spend the night since she had a dream about Ganesha paying her a visit and happily doing the Garba with her. Residents of Gokuldham are unable to determine whether to allow Bhakti to remain in society or not. Bhakti, however, is unwilling to leave without first having Ganpati Bappa play Garba. She also announces that she will not touch any food without meeting Ganpati. Madhavi stands in favor of Bhakti and persuades Bhide and everyone to allow Bhakti to stay in Ganpati Pandal. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

'Oye Champions Ban GayeüòÆ' Cody Rhodes & Jey Uso, John Cena Finally - WWE Fastlane 2023 Highlights

WWE Fastlane 2023 delivered an electrifying spectacle that had fans on the edge of their seats from start to finish. One of the biggest highlights of the night was the unexpected victory of the dynamic duo, Cody Rhodes and Jey Uso, who emerged as the new tag team champions. Their victory at Fastlane 2023 marked a turning point in their careers, solidifying them as a dominant force in the WWE tag team division.
The clash between Cody Rhodes and Jey Uso against their opponents, Judgment Day, was a match for the ages. With high-flying action, incredible teamwork, and an unpredictable finish, it was a contest that will be remembered for years to come.
Fastlane 2023 results showcased the best of WWE's talent roster, with Seth Rollins taking on the enigmatic Shinsuke Nakamura in a thrilling singles bout. The high-stakes encounter had the audience at the edge of their seats, as both superstars left no stone unturned to secure victory.
The entire Fastlane 2023 event, from start to finish, was nothing short of spectacular. Fans who tuned in for the WWE Fastlane 2023 full show were treated to an unforgettable night of sports entertainment. From the opening match to the main event, Fastlane 2023 lived up to its reputation as one of the most exciting pay-per-views on the WWE calendar.
As if the night couldn't get any more exciting, there were even rumors of a surprise appearance by the legendary John Cena, adding an extra layer of anticipation and excitement to the already action-packed Fastlane 2023 highlights. Whether you're a die-hard WWE fan or a casual viewer, Fastlane 2023 was a must-watch event that showcased the best of professional wrestling at its finest.

snippet.title: Kalank Mega Ep 47 - [Eng Sub]  Hira Mani - Junaid Khan - Nazish Jahangir - Sami Khan - 8th Oct 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kalank Mega Ep 47 - [Eng Sub]  Hira Mani - Junaid Khan - Nazish Jahangir - Sami Khan - 8th October 2023

"Kalank" follows Sara, a determined MBA graduate seeking a job while living with her parents. Her aunt perceives Sara as a threat to her daughter's wedding prospects, adding tension to their household. Meanwhile, Sara and her cousin Wahaj develop feelings for each other, leading to potential marriage plans.
However, Sara's faces a set of unfortunate events when she joins a new office and encounters Sarfaraz, a manager with malicious intent. He defames and disrespects her, triggering a series of troubles and crises in her professional and personal life.
As false accusations tarnish her reputation, Sara faces an uphill battle to prove her innocence. The drama intensifies as doubts and skepticism surround her. Will she be able to restore her credibility and regain her standing in society? Amidst the chaos, the future of Sara and Wahaj's relationship hangs in the balance. Will their love survive the challenges posed by external forces and family pressure?

Written by: Edison Idrees Masih
Directed by: Mohsin Mirza
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast: 
Hira Mani - Sara
Junaid Khan - Wahaj
Sami Khan - Danyal
Nazish Jahangir - Duriya
Saba Hameed - Shahana
Noor ul Hassan - Asghar
Nazleen Nasar - Hameeda
Ayesha Gul - Romana
Kamran Jilani - Sarfaraz
Zain Afzal - Shahrukh
Sara Umair - Neeni
Alina - Nousheen

Episode 3895: Ganpati Ki Param Bhakt
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone at Gokuldham is relieved when Bhakti regains consciousness, but they are surprised to hear something new about her. Bhakti pleads that the Gokuldham residents allow her to spend the night since she had a dream about Ganesha paying her a visit and happily doing the Garba with her. Bhide dismisses her account, claiming that it must be malevolent in nature. Champaklal advises Bhide to believe the little girl's statements and let her remain. Bhide is certain of his decision since he does not want to jeopardize the safety of the gold chain and silver modak. Watch the episode to find out if Bhakti's request is granted.

snippet.title: Kalank Mega Ep 46 - [Eng Sub]  Hira Mani - Junaid Khan - Nazish Jahangir - Sami Khan - 8th Oct 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kalank Mega Ep 46 - [Eng Sub]  Hira Mani - Junaid Khan - Nazish Jahangir - Sami Khan - 8th October 2023

"Kalank" follows Sara, a determined MBA graduate seeking a job while living with her parents. Her aunt perceives Sara as a threat to her daughter's wedding prospects, adding tension to their household. Meanwhile, Sara and her cousin Wahaj develop feelings for each other, leading to potential marriage plans.
However, Sara's faces a set of unfortunate events when she joins a new office and encounters Sarfaraz, a manager with malicious intent. He defames and disrespects her, triggering a series of troubles and crises in her professional and personal life.
As false accusations tarnish her reputation, Sara faces an uphill battle to prove her innocence. The drama intensifies as doubts and skepticism surround her. Will she be able to restore her credibility and regain her standing in society? Amidst the chaos, the future of Sara and Wahaj's relationship hangs in the balance. Will their love survive the challenges posed by external forces and family pressure?

Written by: Edison Idrees Masih
Directed by: Mohsin Mirza
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: ‡¥∏‡µá‡¥Æ‡¥ø‡¥Ø ‡¥â‡¥™‡µç‡¥™‡µÅ‡¥Æ‡¥æ‡¥µ‡µç | Semiya Upma Malayalam Recipe | Vermicelli Uppumavu | Easy Kerala Breakfast Recipe
snippet.description:
"Semiya Uppumavu" is a delightful and wholesome South Indian dish, predominantly savored as a breakfast or snack. As you embark on preparing this delicious recipe, the captivating aroma of roasted Vermicelli, also known as vermicelli, immediately fills the kitchen, promising a delightful culinary experience ahead. This dish is noted for its simplicity, requiring minimal ingredients and time, making it a favorite amongst individuals leading busy lives.
The process begins with roasting the thin, noodle-like semiya until it attains a beautiful golden hue. The roasted Vermicelli is then combined with a tempting mixture of finely chopped vegetables, chilies, and aromatic spices, ensuring a balance of flavors that dance on the palate. The addition of mustard seeds, urad dal, and curry leaves in hot oil introduces a layer of texture and fragrance that elevates the dish to new heights.
Semiya Upma is not only a pleasure for the taste buds but also a visually appealing dish, presenting a burst of vibrant colors from the mixed vegetables and delicate, golden strands of Vermicelli. This nutritious meal is further enriched with the goodness of vegetables, making it a perfect choice for individuals seeking a balance of taste and health in their diet.
As you enjoy the video, you‚Äôll notice how each step in crafting Semiya Uppumavu is executed with care and precision, ensuring a perfect outcome every time. Lyrics:
To the principal ji, gaur naal suno gall ji.
College ch saal mera aakhari, haul pende ajkal ji. Zara nigah maro sade wal ji.
Visha aarzi da yaara diya yaariyan, iss aarzi nu kro parvaan ji. Gaal modeyo na dil fail honge. Pass kr lange sare imtihan ji.
Hove na dilan da nuksan ji, enna tusi rakhao  dhyan ji, shreeman ji. Meri binti management nu, sada camp ek hor lagva dio. Dur lejo ji phadan val nu, yaadgari  photoaan vi krva dao. Sade sera toh thakan jehi la dao.

I beg to say time very less jii. Sach akhdaan mazak ni mein karda. Tussi maapeya jahe ho saade guru ho, todhi  nuhn bina ve na mera sarda. Sacche dilon ohde utte marda. Teen saal toh pyaar ohnu  krda.
Ek bojh hai kitaaban da dimaag teh, dujha  maarle vichodeya de darr ne. Tussi khudh  dekhi college di zindagi tuhade bina sade dukh kinne harne.
Dilan ne ve laaye paane dharne, kidda masla  gambhir khada dekhlo. Kro hukum tan hove haal ji.

To the principal jii, hun meenta te aagyi gaal ji. Seva vekhe aa principal ji meenta teh aagyi gaal ji.
College ch saal mera aakhari haul pende aajkal ji, zara nigha maro saade val jii.

In the Hangzhou 2022 Asian Games, India and Bangladesh faced each other in the men's cricket event. India won the toss and elected to bowl first. A strong bowling performance from team India restricted Bangladesh to just 96 runs at the end of their innings. India later chased down the target in just 9.2 overs, thanks to Ruturaj Gaikwad and Tilak Varma.

snippet.title: Israel warns Gaza to prepare for retaliation following surprise attack - BBC News
snippet.description:
Israel has warned Gazans to prepare for retaliation after an unprecedented attack on the country by Hamas left a reported 250 people dead. 

Israel‚Äôs Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu said the country has entered a "long and difficult war".

Since the initial attack, Israel has been striking targets in the Gaza Strip, and has advised people there to take shelter. 

More than 230 Gazans have been killed and 1,000 others wounded so far, according to Palestinian officials.
